casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Liebtag, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Liebtag (1994), 71 Ohio St.3d 167.]

*168(No. 94-1473 Submitted October 24, 1994 Decided December 14, 1994.) Craig L. Liebtag, pro se. Per Curiam.

The decision of the court of appeals is affirmed for the reasons stated therein.

Judgment affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur. Wright, J., dissents.
